                  <p class="- topic/p ">1 common alarm output relays</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">2 free programmable output relays</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">1 EPO input contact</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
