               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">1 battery temperature input and/or ambient temperature (free
programmable)</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Assignment</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">All of the input contacts and
output relays can be assigned to functions and alarms by configuration
(no fixed assignments). The Emergency Power OFF (EPO) is an exception
as it is always assigned as shown in the connection diagram for the
external connection board. There are two connection options:</p>
